title: Donnell Rawlings

description:
Whitney and Donnell hang out and discuss comedy in the time of Covid, his tiny dog Maggie, Chappelle, and moisturizer. You know and love Donnell from Chappelle's Show, The Wire, and his riotous stand-up.
